📄 PRODUCT REQUIREMENT DOCUMENT (PRD)
Product: Insta Auto DM Frontend
1. 🎯 Goal

Build a clean, minimal, white-themed web app where users can:

Connect their Instagram
Set up automated DMs
Manage conversations and campaigns
Track performance

Focus: simple UI, fast actions, no clutter

2. 👤 Target Users
Creators (Reels/Content creators)
Small businesses
Agencies managing multiple accounts
3. 🎨 Design Direction (IMPORTANT)
Primary color: White (#FFFFFF)
Accent: Black / Dark Gray (#111 / #333)
Secondary: Soft Gray (#F5F5F5)
Highlight: Blue (#3B82F6) or Purple (#7C3AED)
UI Style:
Clean cards
Rounded corners (12px–16px)
Soft shadows
Lots of spacing
Minimal text
4. 🧩 CORE PAGES (Step-by-Step)
4.1 🔐 Auth Pages

Pages:

Login
Signup

Features:

Email + password
“Continue with Instagram” (main CTA)
Forgot password
4.2 🏠 Dashboard (Main Screen)

Purpose: Quick overview

Sections:

Connected account info
Active automations
Messages sent today
Growth stats

Components:

Stat cards
Recent activity
Quick actions:
➕ Create Automation
📩 View Messages
4.3 🤖 Automation Builder (CORE FEATURE)

This is your main money feature.

Page Type: Form + Preview

Features:

Trigger selection:
Comment on post
New follower
Keyword in DM
Message input (with variables like {name})
Delay settings (optional)
CTA buttons (links)

UI Blocks:

Left: Settings
Right: Live preview (Instagram-style chat UI)
4.4 📋 Automation List Page

Purpose: Manage all automations

Features:

List view (cards or table)
Toggle ON/OFF
Edit / Delete
Status (Active / Paused)
4.5 💬 Messages / Inbox

Purpose: View conversations

Features:

Chat list (left sidebar)
Chat window (right)
Search users
Filters:
Unread
Replied
Automated
4.6 📊 Analytics Page

Purpose: Show performance

Metrics:

Messages sent
Open rate
Reply rate
Conversion clicks

UI:

Graphs
Daily/weekly toggle
Campaign-wise breakdown
4.7 👤 Account Settings

Sections:

Profile info
Connected Instagram account
Logout
Notifications
4.8 🔌 Integrations (Optional but powerful)

Future-ready page

Integrations:

Zapier
Webhooks
Email tools
4.9 💳 Billing (If SaaS)

Features:

Plan selection
Usage limits
Upgrade/downgrade
5. 🧱 COMPONENTS YOU’LL NEED
Reusable Components:
Navbar (top)
Sidebar (left)
Card UI
Buttons (Primary / Secondary)
Input fields
Toggle switch
Modal (for create/edit)
Toast notifications
6. 🔄 USER FLOW
Flow 1: New User
Signup
Connect Instagram
Go to Dashboard
Create Automation
Activate
Flow 2: Daily Use
Open Dashboard
Check stats
View messages
Optimize automation
7. ⚡ MUST-HAVE FEATURES (MVP)
Instagram connect
Automation builder
Automation toggle ON/OFF
Basic analytics
Message inbox
8. 🚀 NICE-TO-HAVE (PHASE 2)
AI message suggestions
A/B testing
Bulk campaigns
Multi-account support
Templates marketplace
9. 🧠 UX RULES (VERY IMPORTANT)
Keep forms short
Show preview everywhere
Avoid too many clicks
Use icons + minimal text
Everything should feel fast
10. 🛠️ TECH SUGGESTION (for you)

Since you're already using React:

